<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Breath of Darkness (闇の呼吸)</h1>
    <p>Official site of the Dark Breathing Style</p>
  </header>  <section>
    <h2>Origin of the Breath</h2>
    <p>
      The Breath of Darkness (闇の呼吸 - Yami no Kokyū) was born from grief and vengeance. It was created by a legendary demon slayer named Alet, who mastered both the Flame and Moon Breathing Styles. After losing her two children during a demon hunt, Alet merged the two techniques into a single, terrifying form: black flame — a fire that gives no light.
    </p>
  </section>  <section>
    <h2>Creator of the Breath</h2>
    <p>
      Alet (アレット) is the sole creator of the Breath of Darkness. Consumed by sorrow and rage after the death of her children, she turned away from her humanity and embraced undeath, becoming part demon herself. Her new breath was forged purely for vengeance.
    </p>
    <p>
      Alet never had students and did not teach her style to anyone. Her only purpose was to hunt down the demon who destroyed her family.
    </p>
  </section>  <section>
    <h2>Breaths Combined</h2>
    <p>
      The Breath of Darkness is a fusion of:
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Fire Breathing (火の呼吸)</strong>: raw power and fiery destruction.</li>
        <li><strong>Moon Breathing (月の呼吸)</strong>: illusion, grace, and deadly elegance.</li>
      </ul>
      Together, they formed a black flame capable of consuming body and soul.
    </p>
  </section>  <section>
    <h2>Styles of the Breath of Darkness</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>🌹 <strong>Black Rose Hurricane</strong> (黒薔薇の嵐, *Kurobara no Arashi*) — Wind technique that unleashes a storm of dark petals.</li>
      <li>🔊 <strong>Empty Sound</strong> (虚音, *Kyonē*) — Silent strike that confuses the enemy.</li>
      <li>🔥 <strong>Flame of Darkness</strong> (闇の炎, *Yami no Honō*) — Core technique, a soul-burning black fire.</li>
      <li>💔 <strong>Broken Heart</strong> (砕けた心, *Kudaketa Kokoro*) — Love-based strike channeling inner sorrow.</li>
      <li>💧 <strong>Oil Water</strong> (油水, *Abura Mizu*) — Sticky, suffocating water attack of darkness.</li>
      <li>🦋 <strong>Poison Butterfly</strong> (毒蝶, *Dokuchō*) — Insect technique, swift and deadly like venomous wings.</li>
      <li>🌫️ <strong>Mist Smoke</strong> (霧煙, *Kiri Kemuri*) — Mist technique that conceals all movement.</li>
      <li>🪨 <strong>Stone Wall</strong> (石壁, *Ishikabe*) — Rock-solid defense against demonic force.</li>
      <li>🌘 <strong>Solar Eclipse</strong> (日蝕, *Nisshoku*) — Sun technique that suppresses all light.</li>
      <li>🌑 <strong>Vanished Moon</strong> (失月, *Shitsugetsu*) — Moon technique used for stealth and ambush.</li>
      <li>🐍 <strong>Three-Headed Serpent</strong> (三頭蛇, *Santō Ja*) — Triple-directional snake-like strikes.</li>
      <li>🐾 <strong>Beast Claws</strong> (獣の爪, *Kemono no Tsume*) — Savage attack mimicking a beast’s fury.</li>
      <li>⚡ <strong>Ball Lightning</strong> (球雷, *Kyūrai*) — Fast-moving arc strike of thunder.</li>
      <li>🌿 <strong>Vines of Death</strong> (死の蔓, *Shi no Tsuru*) — Floral technique of shadowy vines that choke enemies.
    </ul>
  </section>  <footer>
